description: Beneath a varnished golden oak ceiling, a simple floral tapestry hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A large set of carved haon hooks and a large cherrywood cabinet sit in opposite corners while a tiered alabaster fountain rests on a polished oak floor.

Beneath a varnished golden oak ceiling, a simple floral tapestry hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  Some hammered copper display hooks and a set of carved felwood shelves sit in opposite corners while a tiered alabaster fountain rests on a polished oak floor.
title: [Laphrael's General Store]
